Intro to Pointers

Arrays and Vectors- 1D data structures containing the elements. list of data values, inside them we can store multipke values.
The memory section in which they are stored as arrays are statically allocated(STACK) and vectors are dynamically allocated(HEAP- intro to pointers in c and cpp prpgramming simultaneously) 
